# Trade Journal

*Append-only. Every trade gets an entry — wins and losses alike.*
*Copy this file to JOURNAL.md to initialise: `cp memory/JOURNAL.md.example memory/JOURNAL.md`*

---

## Format

```
Date | Symbol | Direction | Entry ₹ | Exit ₹ | Qty | P&L ₹ | R multiple
Thesis: [Why I entered]
What happened: [Factual description of how the trade played out]
Lesson: [One concrete thing I learned or confirmed]
```

